Incorrect, since you don't update days_in_year on each loop iteration. If you really want...<p><pre><code>    while (days > (days_in_year = IsLeapYear(year) ? 366 : 365)) {
        days -= days_in_year;
        year += 1;
    }</code></pre>

I prefer:<p><pre><code>  for (;;) {
    int days_in_year = IsLeapYear(year) ? 366 : 365;
    if (days <= days_in_year) break;
    days -= days_in_year;
    year += 1;
  }</code></pre>
